text:
East River, at the foot of East 33rd Street, showing the ferry slip of the Borden Ave., Long Island City Ferry. Also shown (background, right to left) are; the News, Chrysler, Chanin and Lincoln Buildings. This is a set of two views taken from pier 81, at the foot of East 33rd Street.

June 16, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.
title: East River - Piers.
